reviewText: got it to watch the short film "last exit" so i really like it.
You will enjoy this movie it's very good

I enjoyed all the short stories.  Some of them left me wondering what happened next...while the ending credits rolled.  However, I really liked having different stories on one dvd representing different cultures during various time periods.

I just bought the DVD "She likes Girls 2" and the first short documentary is an 11 minute GEM titled "High Heels on Wheels". This is a great inside look at women's empowerment long before there was such a word or idea featuring old clips of black and white Roller Derby. This documentary is fun and inspiring.
